illini mens track and field junior Cody Wisslead saw his season end June  at the USA Championships PERIOD

The junior fell just short of advancing in the 400meter hurdles as his time of . seconds placed him ninth  one spot out of the finals PERIOD South Floridas David Aristil nabbed the eighth and final qualifying spot with a time of . seconds while Nikes Bershawn Jackson ran the top time of the day . pERIOD

The weekend marked the second straight championship race in which Wisslead narrowly missed a shot at the finals PERIOD Two weeks ago at the NCAA Championships Wisslead missed the  hurdles finals by two spots PERIOD
title: Wisslead falls short at USA Championships - The Daily Illini
name: University of Illinois Urbana Champaign
